org.apache.tephra

Class AbstractTransactionExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.tephra.AbstractTransactionExecutor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TransactionExecutor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultTransactionExecutor

    public abstract class AbstractTransactionExecutor
extends Object
implements TransactionExecutor
    Provides implementation of asynchronous methods of TransactionExecutor by delegating their execution to respective synchronous methods via provided ExecutorService.
